definition Matrix.IsDiagonalizable {n : Type u_2} [Fintype n] {𝕜 : Type u_1} [Field 𝕜] [DecidableEq n] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), Invertible P ∧ (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P).IsDiag

definition Matrix.IsDiagonalizable {n : Type u_2} {α : Type u_1} [Field α] [DecidableEq n] [Fintype n]
  (A : Matrix n n α) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n α), P.det ≠ 0 ∧ ∃ (D : Matrix n n α), IsDiagonal D ∧ P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P = D

definition Matrix.IsDiagonalizable {α : Type u_1} [Field α] {n : Type u_4} [Fintype n] [DecidableEq n] (A : Matrix n n α) :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n α), Invertible P ∧ (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P).IsDiag

definition Matrix.IsDiagonalizable {n : Type u} [Fintype n] {𝕜 : Type v} [Field 𝕜] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), IsInvertible P ∧ Matrix.isDiag (P⁻¹ * A * P)

definition Matrix.IsDiagonalizable {n : Type u_2} [Fintype n] [DecidableEq n] (A : Matrix n n ℂ) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n ℂ), IsInvertible P ∧ ∃ (D : Matrix n n ℂ), IsDiagonal D ∧ P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P = D

definition Matrix.IsDiagonalizable {n : Type u_2} {𝕜 : Type u_1} [Field 𝕜] [DecidableEq n] [Fintype n] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), P.det ≠ 0 ∧ ∃ (D : Matrix n n 𝕜), D.IsDiag ∧ P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P = D

def Matrix.IsDiagonalizable {n : Type u_1} [Fintype n] [DecidableEq n] {𝕜 : Type u_2} [Field 𝕜] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), Invertible P ∧ Matrix.fromBlocks (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P).IsDiag

definition Matrix.IsDiagonalizable {n : Type u} {α : Type v} [Field α] [DecidableEq n] [Fintype n] (A : Matrix n n α) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n α), P.invertible ∧ (P⁻¹ * A * P).IsDiag

definition Matrix.Diagonalizable {α : Type u} [Field α] {n : Type v} [Fintype n] [DecidableEq n] (A : Matrix n n α) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n α), (∃ (P_inv : Matrix n n α), P ⬝ P_inv = 1 ∧ P_inv ⬝ P = 1) ∧
  ∃ (D : Matrix n n α), D.IsDiag ∧ P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P = D

def Matrix.isDiagonalizable {n : Type u} [Fintype n] [DecidableEq n] {𝕜 : Type v} [Field 𝕜] {A : Matrix n n 𝕜} :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), P.det ≠ 0 ∧ (P⁻¹ * A * P).IsDiag

def Matrix.diagonalizable {n : Type u} [Fintype n] {𝕜 : Type v} [CommRing 𝕜] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), Invertible P ∧ ∃ (D : Matrix n n 𝕜), D.IsDiag ∧ P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P = D

definition Matrix.IsDiagonalizable {α : Type u_1} [Field α] [DecidableEq α] {n : Type u_2} [Fintype n] (A : Matrix n n α) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n α), P.Invertible ∧ Matrix.IsDiag (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)

def Matrix.diagonalizable {n : Type u_2} [Fintype n] (A : Matrix n n ℂ) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n ℂ), P.det ≠ 0 ∧ isDiag (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)

def Matrix.IsDiagonalizable {n : Type u_4} {𝕜 : Type u_1} [Field 𝕜] [DecidableEq n] [Fintype n] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), Invertible P ∧ (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P).IsDiag

def Matrix.diagonalizable {n : Type u_4} [Fintype n] {𝕜 : Type u_1} [Field 𝕜] [DecidableEq n] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜) [Invertible P], Matrix.isDiagonal (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)

definition Matrix.IsDiagonalizable : ∀ {n : Type u_1} {𝕜 : Type u_2} [inst : Field 𝕜] [inst_1 : DecidableEq n], Matrix n n 𝕜 → Prop :=
  λ {n 𝕜} [Field 𝕜] [DecidableEq n] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜),
    ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), P.det ≠ 0 ∧ (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P).IsDiag

def Matrix.isDiagonalizable {n : Type u} [Fintype n] [DecidableEq n] {𝕜 : Type v} [Field 𝕜] (A : Matrix n n 𝕜) :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n 𝕜), P.det ≠ 0 ∧ (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P).IsDiag

definition Matrix.isDiagonalizable {n : Type u} [Fintype n] {α : Type v} [Field α] (A : Matrix n n α) : Prop :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n α), IsUnit P ∧ (∃ (D : Matrix n n α), D.IsDiag ∧ P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P = D)
